      "id": "PopularPost101851",
      "post_content": "This does not seem like a good card. If your opponent plays *any* creature that isn't the same color as yours, yes even *just one*, you have an enchantment that does nothing. If you are playing against an opponent running creatures that all share one color, then chances are they are also playing a creature-heavy aggro deck except they will run non stupid cards that only affect their creatures, like [glorious anthem](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=glorious anthem) or [honor of the pure](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=honor of the pure) or [marshal's anthem](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=marshal's anthem).  \n  \nAlthough, it would be funny in multiplayer when everyone groups up on whoever is off color.  ",
      "posted_by": "allmighty_abacus",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost101851\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">This does not seem like a good card. If your opponent plays <i>any</i> creature that isn't the same color as yours, yes even <i>just one</i>, you have an enchantment that does nothing. If you are playing against an opponent running creatures that all share one color, then chances are they are also playing a creature-heavy aggro deck except they will run non stupid cards that only affect their creatures, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"glorious anthem\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=glorious anthem\">glorious anthem</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"honor of the pure\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=honor of the pure\">honor of the pure</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"marshal's anthem\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=marshal's anthem\">marshal's anthem</a>.<br/><br/>Although, it would be funny in multiplayer when everyone groups up on whoever is off color.<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '101851'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy21705\">allmighty_abacus</span>\r\n                                (9/13/2010 1:01:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRa