    {
      "id": "PopularPost68020",
      "post_content": "Mrredhatter is wrong; this card doesn't do anything nearly that cool.   \n  \nHmmm... [Hour of Reckoning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hour of Reckoning), perhaps? Or maybe [Martial Coup](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Martial Coup)? Leave Common Cause on the field for a few turns, build up an a few tokens, then wipe the board and swing through with your army of 3/3s?   \n  \nOtherwise, [Thran Forge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thran Forge) or [Neurok Transmuter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Neurok Transmuter) would both stop opponents creatures from counting towards your +2/+2 bonus. It's not a good combo, but it would make your opponent go lol. ",
      "posted_by": "ScissorsLizard",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost68020\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Mrredhatter is wrong; this card doesn't do anything nearly that cool. <br/><br/>Hmmm... <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hour of Reckoning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hour of Reckoning\">Hour of Reckoning</a>, perhaps? Or maybe <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Martial Coup\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Martial Coup\">Martial Coup</a>? Leave Common Cause on the field for a few turns, build up an a few tokens, then wipe the board and swing through with your army of 3/3s? <br/><br/>Otherwise, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thran Forge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thran Forge\">Thran Forge</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Neurok Transmuter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Neurok Transmuter\">Neurok Transmuter</a> would both stop opponents creatures from counting towards your +2/+2 bonus. It's not a good combo, but it would make your opponent go lol. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '68020'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1310\">ScissorsLizard</span>\r\n                                (4/22/2010 10:58:01 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">